			<node ID="ID_755138205" TEXT="Software development is the process of conceiving specifying designing programming documenting testing and bug fixing involved in creating and maintaining applications frameworks or other software components.Software development is a process of writing and maintaining the source code but in a broader sense it includes all that is involved between the conception of the desired " />
